Date: 1995-06-08

Title: Explicit connection between conformal field theory and 2+1 Chern-Simons

theoryAuthors: D.C.Cabra and G.L.Rossini

Comments: 13 pages, Latex file. To appear in Mod.Phys.Lett.A

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A12 (1997) 1687-1697

We give explicit field theoretical representations for the observables of 2+1dimensional Chern-Simons theory in terms of gauge invariant composites of 2DWZW fields. To test our identification we compute some basic Wilson loopcorrelators reobtaining known results.